Shut your mouth.

824
00:59:12,590 --> 00:59:14,289
I could rip it out.

825
00:59:14,489 --> 00:59:16,989
Yes, this is it.

826
00:59:17,159 --> 00:59:18,829
This is the real you.

827
00:59:20,400 --> 00:59:21,699
You...

828
00:59:21,960 --> 00:59:24,230
