Didn't you?

830
00:59:26,630 --> 00:59:29,369
Don't hide like a coward
and tell me...

831
00:59:29,369 --> 00:59:30,969
that's why you killed people.

832
00:59:30,969 --> 00:59:32,639
Shut your mouth, you scum!

833
00:59:33,880 --> 00:59:35,139
What do you know?

834
00:59:35,809 --> 00:59:38,710
What do you know about
