835
00:59:39,380 --> 00:59:41,079
What do you know?

836
00:59:41,219 --> 00:59:42,650
What do you know?

837
00:59:54,599 --> 00:59:55,699
Kang Dong Jun,

838
00:59:56,360 --> 00:59:57,400
listen to me carefully.

839
00:59:58,469 --> 01:00:00,369
Just like what you said,

840
01:00:00,500 --> 01:00:02,739
